high_descs: Turn to the left and face the desk.
Pick up the clock from the back of the desk.
Carry the clock and turn to the right. Turn to the left and then face the desk on the left.
Hold the clock and turn on the lamp on the right side of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Hold the clock and turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around completely, then turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the clock that is on the desk.
Turn to the right, walk almost to the top of the bed, turn left, walk to the wall, then turn left again to face the desk.
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine an alarm clock using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and face the desk
Grab the canteen off of the desk
Turn right and find the desk with the lamp
anns.task_desc: Turning on a lamp while holding a canteen
